General build requirements:
Python 2.7.x
setuptools (Python module)
cx_Freeze (Python module)
PySide (Python module)
PyWin32 (Python module - Windows only)

To build a directory with an executable and other files inside it:
	python setup.py build
	Directory is named "build\exe.win32-2.7\"
	Copy/zip directory to share
	
For a Windows .msi:
	python setup.py bdist_msi
	It's in "dist\"

On Mac OS X, for a Mac disk image: <= UNTESTED
	python setup.py bdist_dmg

Windows installer:
NSIS Installer (http://nsis.sourceforge.net/Main_Page)
bdist_nsi (Python module)

Project is in Eclipse format.
